{"word":"G1522 - εἰσακούω - eisakoúō - ice-ak-oo'-o - Hear","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἰσακούω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eisakoúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ice-ak-oo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hear</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - செவிகொடு"},{"paragraph":"to hearken unto, to give ear to"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1519 - εἰς - eis - ice/1519\">G1519</a> and <a href=\"#/G191 - ἀκούω - akoúō - ak-oo'-o/191\">G191</a>; to <i>listen</i> to: - hear.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1522/1522\">G1522</a>, <a href=\"#/G1873/1873\">G1873</a>, <a href=\"#/G189/189\">G189</a>, <a href=\"#/G191/191\">G191</a>, <a href=\"#/G3876/3876\">G3876</a>, <a href=\"#/G3878/3878\">G3878</a>, <a href=\"#/G5218/5218\">G5218</a>, <a href=\"#/G5219/5219\">G5219</a>, <a href=\"#/G5255/5255\">G5255</a>"}]}